plot: Caleb accepts Marie's bounty to kill the man who murdered her father. When Caleb returns to confess his love, Marie is nowhere to be found. Meanwhile a dangerous warrior secretly hunts Caleb. Will Caleb survive? Will he find Marie?
title: El Rezo
